Package: lantern
Type: Package
Title: Ancestry-Specific Rare Variant Association Analysis
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Yu",
           family = "Wang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "wangyu19940804@gmail.com")
Description: Ancestry-specific rare variant burden testing for admixed
    populations. Uses a pure C backend to split genotype dosages by local
    ancestry inferred from phased or unphased data, then runs
    ancestry-stratified SMMAT gene-level tests via GMMAT.
URL: https://yuw444.github.io/LANTERN/, https://github.com/yuw444/LANTERN
Additional_repositories: https://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc
    https://bioconductor.org/packages/release/data/annotation
SystemRequirements: bcftools (>= 1.10)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Imports:
    data.table,
    SeqArray
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    GMMAT,
    knitr,
    pkgdown,
